      "name": "Blank",
      "images": [],
      "summary": "The Blank card defines a flexible component for creating and managing decks of cards within a workspace. It allows users to add cards to a deck, view the deck and its total contents in an isolated view, shuffle the deck, and draw individual cards. The component records the sequence and position of each card, supporting duplicates with unique identification, enabling code to recognize and interact with specific card sequences. Its primary purpose is to facilitate sequence-aware card collections for tasks such as customizable decks or ordered card management.",
